The Crypto Express8S feature occupies one I/O slot in a PCIe+ I/O drawer. Each adapter can be configured as a Secure IBM CCA coprocessor, a Secure IBM Enterprise PKCS #11 (EP11) coprocessor, or as an accelerator. Crypto Express8S provides domain support for up to 40 logical partitions. The accelerator function is designed for maximum-speed Secure Sockets Layer and Transport Layer Security (SSL/TLS) acceleration, rather than for specialized financial applications for secure, long-term storage of keys or secrets.
